g.id: Easily grant your employees access by adding them manually or uploading a bulk list for quick approval. The admin dashboard allows you to manage employee accounts effortlessly, ensuring only authorized users can access the meditation app. Approve new employees individually or all at once, saving time and streamlining the onboarding process. Keep your team engaged with seamless access to premium meditation content.
